{"type":null,"faqId":37069,"title":"为什么在使用B2进行蓝牙通话的时候，容易出现一些杂音、电流声、声音断续的情况？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 0.9111111in 1.25in 1.0in 1.25in;}\n.p1{text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:宋体;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span>杂音一般是由环境干扰造成的，例如手机接入wifi的情况下进行蓝牙通话,或者附近有功率较大的路由器,及类似微波炉等微波环境等。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>蓝牙技术是近距离/超低辐射的传输技术，在使用耳机蓝牙通话过程中，有几个建议：</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>1、请保持您的手机和B2在3-5m之内且没有大的物体遮挡和隔离；</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>2、建议通话过程中将耳机和手机放在身体同侧，防止信号被遮挡造成杂音或声音断续的情况；</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>3、确认下周围环境情况，通话效果不好，建议先关掉手机wifi或流量数据，或者远离微波源（如微波炉等）或者先暂时远离大功率路由器；</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>工程师仍在继续优化音频算法，在后续的版本中持续优化通话质量和蓝牙通话稳定性。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>如果平时通话都正常，偶尔会出现杂音，基本确定是环境干扰造成，如果一直有杂音则建议到售后服务处理。</span>\n</p>\n<p  ></p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":209,"faqType":"连接与配对","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"2233","faqTypeCode":"Wearable_Device-Connection-Paring","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1440750141000,"seriesProductName":"B2","visitedTimes":116,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"华为手环,B2,蓝牙通话,通话质量,杂音 ,电流声,声音断续","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}